# Source-document INDEX (added 2026-05-06 by inspector-source-docs during memory-system-uplift).
# Contains 3,211 paths to scattered local PDFs/statements/contracts including
# 747 AstraZeneca work-product paths (~23%). Indexing was authorized by Alton;
# publishing the path manifest to the GitHub DR mirror requires AZ Compliance
# review first. Until then the INDEX stays untracked locally only.
sartor/memory/source-documents/

# Archived predecessor / parallel-fork repos brought in 2026-05-08 during the
# C:\Users\alto8 -> Sartor-claude-network migration. Each carries its own
# inner .git and is preserved as a frozen historical reference, not as live
# project content. Keeping them on disk for backup but out of this repo's
# git tracking. The 376 MB analysis fork would dominate the repo otherwise.
/archive/home-agent-2026-04/
/archive/sartor-network-analysis-2026-12-20-fork/

# Phase 5b archive of seven research / sibling projects pulled in from the
# home dir on 2026-05-08. Treated as frozen historical reference. The two
# trees that had their own .git (predictive-safety-platform,
# safety-research-system) had it removed so the parent repo can track
# their contents normally — losing the project's own commit history but
# preserving the working-tree state. The Playwright browser profile
# (playwright-sandbox/profile/) gitignored because it can contain live
# cookies/session tokens. Drive ignore list will need a parallel entry
# for the profile when sync turns on.
/archive/research-projects-2026-05-08/playwright-sandbox/profile/
